  "texts": [
    "Through this we create a robust labeled and detailed dataset for benchmark or training LLMs to evaluation, and identify key strengths, weaknesses, and potential failure cases in LLMbased email threat detection.",
    "The study addresses the following research questions:",
    "• RQ1: How effectively can LLMs identify emotional strategies and patterns used within email content?",
    "• RQ2: How effectively can LLMs identify motivational strategies and patterns used within email content?",
    "• RQ3: How effectively can a state-of-theart LLM perform email classification of phishing, spam, and legitimate emails across both human-written and LLMgenerated content?"
  ],
